    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Spend less time cooking and make dinner work around you.</strong></p><p>Before you begin, get all your ingredients and equipment ready</p><p>Skim through these steps, then wash your fruit and veg</p><p>You can only heat your food once, then enjoy straight away</p><p>Note: Microwave ovens vary. Make sure you heat food thoroughly (even if it takes you a little longer than 10 min)</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/falafel-and-roast-pepper-couscous-bowl-with-romesco-yoghurt/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Drain your <strong>roasted red peppers</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>couscous</strong> to a medium heatproof bowl with your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong>, <strong>drained roasted red peppers</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/falafel-and-roast-pepper-couscous-bowl-with-romesco-yoghurt/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add 200ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [300ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [400ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong>, cover with a clean tea towel and set aside until all of the liquid has been absorbed</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/falafel-and-roast-pepper-couscous-bowl-with-romesco-yoghurt/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanhile, chop your <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> into quarters</p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong> and pat dry with kitchen paper</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/falafel-and-roast-pepper-couscous-bowl-with-romesco-yoghurt/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>natural yoghurt</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> in a small bowl</p><p>Add your <strong>romesco sauce</strong> and gently swirl through the yoghurt (don't fully mix!) \u2013 this is your <strong>romesco yoghurt</strong></p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/falafel-and-roast-pepper-couscous-bowl-with-romesco-yoghurt/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the couscous has absorbed all the liquid, fluff with a fork and add most of the <strong>chopped cherry tomatoes</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) and your <strong>ground</strong> <strong>sumac</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up \u2013 this is your <strong>roast pepper couscous</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/falafel-and-roast-pepper-couscous-bowl-with-romesco-yoghurt/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>falafel</strong> to a plate and put in the <strong>microwave</strong> for 1-2 min or until warmed</p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/falafel-and-roast-pepper-couscous-bowl-with-romesco-yoghurt/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>warmed falafel</strong> over the <strong>roast pepper couscous</strong> with the <strong>salad</strong> and <strong>remaining chopped cherry tomatoes</strong> to the side</p><p>Drizzle the salad with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Dollop the <strong>romesco yoghurt</strong> over the top and season with a pinch of <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
